Method 1: Using if-else Statements 1
Code:-
year = int(input("Enter Year:"))
if (year%400 == 0) or (year%4==0 and year%100!=0):
  print("Leap Year")
else:
  print("Not a Leap Year")

Output:-
Enter Year:2020
Leap Year


Method 2: Using if-else Statements 2
Code:-
year = int(input("Enter Year: "))
if( ((year % 4 == 0) and (year % 100 != 0)) or (year % 400==0) ):
    print("Leap Year")
else:
    print("Not leap Year")

Output:
Enter Year: 2000
Leap Year
